{"TopicId":206964,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"I see plenty of \u0026#039;moon simulators\u0026#039; but what of the walk?","CreatedByName":"boriz","CreatedById":219053,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-19T00:53:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"boriz","CreatedById":219053,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-19T00:53:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGraphic simulators are abundant, but none I\u0027ve seen, simulate the difficulty that the Apollo astronauts faced just trying to walk.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a low-gravity walking simulator? Something that simulates the difficulty of trying to walk in 1/6th G?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEG: Simulates falling over because you tried to pick up a rock, and the subsequent struggle to get upright. Or simulates the need to adopt a \u0027kangaroo\u0027 bounce, rather than one foot in front of another.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA moon \u003Cstrong\u003Ewalking\u003C/strong\u003E simulator?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-19T00:58:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be pretty fun to set up a 75 degree sloped surface and hang yourself sideways from the top of it, to walk under only the part of Earth\u0027s surface gravity that\u0027s equivalent to the Moon\u0027s.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SunlitZelkova","CreatedById":206402,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-19T01:15:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224093678\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206964\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645231995\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219053\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022boriz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, boriz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA moon \u003Cstrong\u003Ewalking\u003C/strong\u003E simulator?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNASA has already modified the Neutral Buoyancy Laboratory for Artemis training and it has begun. Many months ago they shared a picture on Twitter of an American flag being erected by an astronaut wearing an xEVA suit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-19T05:35:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022220px-Redneckrampage.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022125.00\u0022 height=\u0022275\u0022 width=\u0022220\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/63/Redneckrampage.jpg/220px-Redneckrampage.jpg\u0022\u003E\u00A0after having consumed alcohol beverages (required by the gameplay as a fuel/medicine)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-20T01:54:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224093765\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206964\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645248953\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EReveal hidden contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/63/Redneckrampage.jpg/220px-Redneckrampage.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022220px-Redneckrampage.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022125.00\u0022 height=\u0022275\u0022 width=\u0022220\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/63/Redneckrampage.jpg/220px-Redneckrampage.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0after having consumed alcohol beverages (required by the gameplay as a fuel/medicine)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe in game character or the player ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-20T04:36:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224094059\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206964\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645322054\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257801\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022magnemoe\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, magnemoe said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe in game character or the player ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObligatory for the former, facultative for the latter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(An indicator of alcohol level in blood. The arrow should stay in the middle, green zone.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-23T03:17:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni bought a game in the 90s, forget which, and it had a coupon for a free copy of either that game, or carmageddon.\u00A0 i chose the latter.\u00A0 i do not regret the decision.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-23T03:17:30Z\u0022 title=\u002202/23/2022 03:17  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 23, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}